OL,3,CRochester's MP and Bishop set out
OL,4,Copposing views on assisted dying debate
OL,6,FRochester will soon find itself at the
OL,7,Fforefront of the highly contentious
OL,8,Fdebate over whether to legalise
OL,9,Fassisted dying.
OL,11,FThe Kent town's MP, Lauren Edwards, is
OL,12,Fleading a renewed effort to change the
OL,13,Flaw to allow terminally ill adults to
OL,14,Fbe allowed help to end their lives.
OL,16,FThe Labour MP says this would allow
OL,17,Fpeople a "compassionate choice" while
OL,18,Fensuring "appropriate safeguards".
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@_O]zD@JOUzD@aO]
