PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784796493
OL,3,CRochester's MP and Bishop set out
OL,4,Copposing views on assisted dying debate
OL,6,FLauren Edwards said: "For those people
OL,7,Fwho I've spoken to, many of whom are
OL,8,Fconstituents and from the broader Kent
OL,9,Farea, who are absolutely desperate for
OL,10,Fthis choice, they are people in a lot
OL,11,Fof pain... It's really important that
OL,12,Fthey don't have to fear that
OL,13,Fincredibly painful death that a lot of
OL,14,Fthem are facing."
OL,16,FThe Bishop of Rochester has said he is
OL,17,F"deeply concerned" about the renewed
OL,18,Fattempt to change the law.
OL,26,@nD@VOUvD@QO]yD@AOUyD@RO]
