OL,3,CRochester's MP and Bishop set out
OL,4,Copposing views on assisted dying debate
OL,6,FThe Right Reverend Jonathan Gibbs told
OL,7,FITV News Meridian: "If this kind of
OL,8,Fsystem is introduced, will it not
OL,9,Fchange the relationship between
OL,10,Fsociety and the elderly and the
OL,11,Fvulnerable?
OL,13,F"In particular, those who may face
OL,14,Fsome form of coercion or feel they're
OL,15,Fa burden on society? I think we need
OL,16,Fto weigh very, very carefully the
OL,17,Fimplications of such a huge change."
OL,26,@oD@TOUuD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
