OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1784796493
OL,3,CRochester's MP and Bishop set out
OL,4,Copposing views on assisted dying debate
OL,6,FWhile on different sides of the
OL,7,Fdebate, the Bishop said he'd been in
OL,8,Ftouch with Lauren Edwards, adding: "I
OL,9,Frespect her enormously for the
OL,10,Fconviction and compassion which she
OL,11,Fbrings to this debate."
OL,13,FThe bill proposes allowing adults in
OL,14,FEngland and Wales, with fewer than six
OL,15,Fmonths to live, to apply for an
OL,16,Fassisted death subject to the approval
OL,17,Fof two doctors and an expert panel.
OL,26,@pD@dOUsD@WO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
